30sYYBXj_2GzXLO-XbbD-r1AtPWBewjKQ", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5103AQHJPukmrmxIpg/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/profile-displayphoto-shrink_400_400/0/1516258966643?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=2JfpaM_By230sYYBXj_2GzXLO-XbbD-r1AtPWBewjKQ", "publicIdentifier": "wim-n-m-fagel-hotelier", "recommendations/0/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Hnin Htet on the same team", "recommendations/0/date": "January 22, 2023", "recommendations/0/description": "Ms. Hnin Htet Aung is eager to learn new things which were not in her field. She took action fast and she has an open mind. She has a great personality and always it was a pleasure to work with her!", "recommendations/0/name": "Hnin Htet Aung", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "KMA Real Estate | Planning Parami General Hospital | Director Myanmar Investors Development Association | Secretary", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hnin-htet-aung/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABxbNlcBqevhLdnNwiPITmzyd-_I_qLco4A", "recommendations/1/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Brad but on different teams", "recommendations/1/date": "October 5, 2016", "recommendations/1/description": "Brad is a sales person who knows the markets and come with ideas to increase the occupancy and especially the ADR and revenue. He is a team player and takes the initiative to organise and achieve the set target as soon as possible and  do not wait until the deadline. Brad is a high qualified professional! It is a pleasure to work with Brad.", "recommendations/1/name": "Brad Taylor", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Head of Channel & Distribution | Building EMEA & APJ partner ecosystems that drive revenue | VAR · VAD · Cybersecurity | Trying to save the world! 🌏", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bradleyjtaylor/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANDMGABDwTk6nFawr0WmX2YnQhSOJG9Hqo", "recommendations/2/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Michelle but on different teams", "recommendations/2/date": "August 29, 2016", "recommendations/2/description": "I have had the pleasure of working with Michelle Jamieson while she was the Corporate Director of Marketing Communications at Centara Hotels & Resorts. It was clear from the beginning that Michelle was passionate about what she does and was committed to providing the necessary support and guidance to my team and I, in any capacity. \n \nDuring a trip throughout Europe for a General Managers Roadshow, Michelle demonstrated her understanding of the corporate business as well as connecting all properties to personal stories highlighting their unique positions within the Centara portfolio. She was able to present a cohesive story about Centara’s various brands along with developing the personality of each property. This type of storytelling seems to be innate for Michelle.\n \nMichelle is always positive, professional and very personable, which is vital in her role in communications. I completely trust Michelle’s judgement as it relates to PR, communications and marketing. She provided creative and innovative solutions that were viable given some of the restraints that we might have faced. She also provided opportunities for my staff to grow beyond the everyday activities and helped to initiate some photography and other social media trainings that added to the service quality in our many F&B outlets. Taking into consideration the importance of the two-way communication and engagement desires of guests, Michelle addressed many of those needs through assistance in implementing a social media plan and partnership with an agency to assist in the implementation. \n \nI highly recommend Michelle as she excels in fast-paced environments, thrives on a challenge, is incredibly resourceful when looking for solutions to problems and is effective in identifying opportunities. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Michelle Jamieson", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Storyteller", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mcjamieson/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWPQbcBVFVvYKdg3Ah3t4PzUr9HnWTfq9U", "recommendations/3/context": "Wim N.M. was Martijn's client", "recommendations/3/date": "June 28, 2016", "recommendations/3/description": "Martijn was one of the team members of the Stenden University Bangkok projects. His committee had to set up the Culinary Dutch in Bangkok event during the period 23-30 September 2016 at Centara Grand at Central Plaza Ladprao Bangkok. Martijn was eager to learn new points and was not afraid to ask questions if it was not clear. He has a high potential to be a great manager in the future.", "recommendations/3/name": "Martijn Beerse", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Director of Operations @ Hilton | Operations Management, Hospitality Management", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/martijn-beerse-a0599a61/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA0jXiUBYxHQQCj6Se8mEjnbPxfvBdSaVQY", "recommendations/4/context": "Wim N.M. was Kasper's client", "recommendations/4/date": "April 17, 2012", "recommendations/4/description": "I have worked several times together with Kasper. He is down to earth and he knows his job as recruiter. He does what he promised and on time. If a candidate started in the vacant position then he will follow up how the candidate performs and takes action if necessary Due his great personality he build a huge network and he will assist you if he can. I will not hesitate to work again together with Kasper in the future.", "recommendations/4/name": "Kasper Hemmingshøj", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Head of Talent Acquisition @ Capgemini ♠️ Recruitment Expert Driving Growth", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hemmingshoj/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMQaE8B6Tki52bVfwnuWPSnRqqaq8HRHvc", "recommendations/5/context": "Wim N.M. managed Nattaya directly", "recommendations/5/date": "February 19, 2012", "recommendations/5/description": "Nattaya worked at the Amari Rincome Hotel, Chiang Mai, as Assistant Food & Beverage Manager. She was responsible for all functions in and outside the hotel, never there was any complain of the service of the functions. As well she was in charge of all paperwork. She was highly respected by her staff and supervisor. It was a great pleasure to work together with her.", "recommendations/5/name": "Nattaya Smith", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Executive Assistant to CHRO APM Terminals (A.P. Moller - Maersk) I partner with leaders to lead with humanity, inspiration, and lasting impact", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nattaya-smith-a93842b/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAIU548BptWN1wnIda03ysrQP7ER3rTx9Bw", "recommendations/6/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Yasuhiro but on different teams", "recommendations/6/date": "December 19, 2011", "recommendations/6/description": "It was a great honor to work together with Mr. Yoneyama. He had great ideas how to improve the Japanese marktet in and outside Bangkok. He gave a lot of support during the pre-opening and the opening period of the Amari Residences Bangkok. He takes his responsibilities and is eager to learn more. It was a great pleasure to work together with Mr. Yoneyama.", "recommendations/6/name": "Yasuhiro Yoneyama", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Director of Sales & Marketing at Grand Nikko Bangkok Sathorn - Pre Opening Office", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yasuhiro-yoneyama-6649653a/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhUF2wBwAg5D0-JdngIbk72Oo6EWi8H50s", "recommendations/7/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Christian on the same team", "recommendations/7/date": "July 28, 2010", "recommendations/7/description": "Christian is a down to earth person. He knows exactly what he has to do, he works fast and accurate. Nothing is too much, he will never complain and is friendly all the time. He was involved at several sales projects during the re-branding of Amari Hotels & Resorts, it was always a great pleasure to work togehter with him in these committees.", "recommendations/7/name": "Christian L.", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Luxury & Lifestyle Hospitality Commercial Leader | Revenue Growth, Market Expansion, Strategic Partnerships & Commercial Architecture", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-lueke/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHxPLEBIgmavz9BhvGw4Qz9IVoPIH8_3Uc", "recommendations/8/context": "Wim N.M. worked with Remo on the same team", "recommendations/8/date": "July 5, 2010", "recommendations/8/description": "As General Manager of the Amari Rincome in Chiang Mai and currently as General Manager of Amari Residences in Bangkok I have worked always very closely with Remo. He is open minded is eager to learn more and more. He works always precise. He is a big support to our pre-opening team at Amari Residences Bangkok. It is a joy to work with Remor who understands his job.", "recommendations/8/name": "Remo Kleger", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Senior Manager Financial Services @ Pistor AG", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/remo-kleger-92406712/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJ_-mwBMsFAji1DfjkSxefMMNy7elKLF6I", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Hnin Htet worked with Wim N.M. on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "January 17, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Mr Fagel is very experienced and tip top in his role in setting up in a new destination. ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Hnin Htet Aung", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "KMA Real Estate | Planning Parami General Hospital | Director Myanmar Investors Development Association | Secretary", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hnin-htet-aung/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABxbNlcBqevhLdnNwiPITmzyd-_I_qLco4A", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Michelle worked with Wim N.M. on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "October 16, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "From the time I started at Centara, Wim was a warm and strong leader that provided not only great direction but also partnership.  Working with Wim was always a pleasure as he instilled a sense of confidence in his employees that empowered them to take charge and be creative and innovative in their approaches to solve problems.  There was always an appreciation by Wim when I or his team presented interesting opportunities that would help the hotel reach their goals.  Wim understands the whole hospitality industry which provides him with the ability to see the big picture that pairs with his perfect attention to detail to efficiently and effective provide a very high level of service and partnership with his employees and others.  ", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Michelle Jamieson", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Storyteller", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mcjamieson/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWPQbcBVFVvYKdg3Ah3t4PzUr9HnWTfq9U", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Brad worked with Wim N.M. on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "October 10, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Wim Fagel has been not only an excellent mentor but also a great leader within the Centara group. Wim was the task force leader for many hotels and was so for Centara Ceysands' project in Sri Lanka where his expertise shone through as a guiding light for all departments involved, this I'm sure his where it transpired to Wim becoming the General Manager of Centara's Flagship property, the Centara Grand Lad-Prao. \nHis knowledge has clearly been much to lean on and Wim would be an asset to any organization he is within. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Brad Taylor", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Head of Channel & Distribution | Building EMEA & APJ partner ecosystems that drive revenue | VAR · VAD · Cybersecurity | Trying to save the world! 🌏", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bradleyjtaylor/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANDMGABDwTk6nFawr0WmX2YnQhSOJG9Hqo", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Yasuhiro worked with Wim N.M. on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "February 19, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "He is a highly motivated person who takes ownership of all his rolls. Very positive and aggressive.  He really supported to my market and helped me to expand business. It was honor to work with him.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Yasuhiro Yoneyama", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Director of Sales & Marketing at Grand Nikko Bangkok Sathorn - Pre Opening Office", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yasuhiro-yoneyama-6649653a/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhUF2wBwAg5D0-JdngIbk72Oo6EWi8H50s", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Christian worked with Wim N.M. on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "August 4, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I know Wim as a Colleague, he worked in the capacity as General Manager for different properties. I have no hesitation to highly recommend Wim to any Hospitality organisation , who is looking for a dedicated , passionate and professional Hotel Executive. Beside being a great host as a hotel General Manager, the level of quality attained in his role as opening General Manager is not to be missed.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Christian L.", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Luxury & Lifestyle Hospitality Commercial Leader | Revenue Growth, Market Expansion, Strategic Partnerships & Commercial Architecture", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-lueke/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHxPLEBIgmavz9BhvGw4Qz9IVo